title: Aligarh
subTitle: Ramchandra Siras, a professor on whom a sting operation is carried out to determine his sexual orientation, forms a special bond with the journalist who covers his story.

title: Holiday
subTitle: Muskaan, an unpopular, shy girl, falls for Dino, a charismatic dancer, while on a vacation in Goa with her family. However, things become complicated when her father objects to their relationship.

title: Chakravyuh
subTitle: Kabir infiltrates a Maoist organisation to help Adil Khan, who is a decorated police officer and his friend. As he gets deeper into the organisation, Kabir starts sympathising with the group's plight and starts having second thoughts.

title: Mere Pyare Prime Minister
subTitle: After his mother is raped one night, Kannu, an eight-year-old boy, writes a letter to the prime minister of India and embarks on a journey from Mumbai to Delhi with his two friends.

title: Footfairy
subTitle: A CBI officer investigates a string of gruesome murders committed by a serial killer with a foot festish. However, things take an ugly turn when he gets close to catching the killer.

title: Poorna
subTitle: Poorna Malavath, a 13-year-old girl from Telangana, becomes the youngest female in history to climb and reach the summit of Mount Everest.

title: Half Girlfriend
subTitle: After meeting in college, Madhav is smitten with Riya and falls in love with her. However, after his repeated attempts to win her over, she eventually agrees to become his half girlfriend.

title: Jersey
subTitle: Arjun, a talented but failed cricketer, decides to return to cricket in his late thirties driven by the desire to represent the Indian cricket team and fulfil his son's wish for a jersey as a gift.

title: Gully Boy
subTitle: The life of an underdog rapper from Dharavi who struggles to express his views on social issues through rapping, changes completely after he bumps into Shrikant alias MC Sher.

title: Jawaani Jaaneman
subTitle: Jazz, a 40-year-old man, leads a frivolous casanova lifestyle in London. However, when Tia, a young woman claiming to be his daughter, enters his life, he decides to mend his ways.

title: Mission Raniganj: The Great Bharat Rescue
subTitle: Jaswant Singh Gill, a mining engineer, leads a challenging rescue mission to save 65 miners trapped in a flooded coal mine.

title: Beyond the Clouds
subTitle: Tara inadvertently sets the wheels in motion for a life-altering, unsavoury occurrence after she seeks help from the wrong person to protect her drug-dealing brother from the police.

title: Turtle
subTitle: Ramkaran tirelessly churns the dry earth of a village in Rajasthan for water. Meanwhile, the villagers participate in desperate measures to satisfy their thirst.

title: Welcome to New York
subTitle: A recovery agent and a designer become part of a big Bollywood event in New York, where chaos ensues, changing their lives forever.

title: Iqbal
subTitle: Iqbal, a speech and hearing impaired boy, wishes to play cricket for the Indian team but his impairment overshadows his talent. Thus, he seeks help from a former cricket player to train him.

title: Sonchiriya
subTitle: After their leader's death, a group of dacoits splits up and runs away. On the way, they meet two women and help them escape their family and reach the hospital.

title: Faraaz
subTitle: Five terrorists take the staff and customers of Holey Artisan cafe in Dhaka hostage. Faraaz and his friends are among the hostages as the police try to de-escalate the situation.

title: Gold
subTitle: Tapan Das, a passionate team manager with a penchant for alcohol, embarks a ragtag group of hockey players on an ambitious quest for independent India's first Olympic gold medal.

title: Uri: The Surgical Strike
subTitle: Major Vihaan Singh Shergill of the Indian Army leads a covert operation against a group of militants who attacked a base in Uri, Kashmir, in 2016 and killed many soldiers.

title: Trapped
subTitle: A desperate Shaurya moves into an empty high-rise building where he and his lover can stay. However, things take a dark turn when he finds himself locked in his new apartment without any amenities.

title: Kismat Konnection
subTitle: Raj, an out-of-luck architect, and Priya, an out-of-love social activist, find themselves connected in a strange way by destiny.

title: Dhadak
subTitle: A world of uncertainties awaits Madhu and Parthavi as their love transcends class divides and blossoms despite the fierce disapproval of their families.

title: Khaali Peeli
subTitle: Torn apart as young lovers, Pooja and Blackie's lives take different paths. Fate brings them back together after Pooja's courageous escape from a brothel.
